.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: coral, fuchsia, light-brown, chestnut, brown
There are 5 different nationalities: egyptian, russian, dutch, chinese, italian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo, davidoff, bolivar, dannemann
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-mirinda, mirinda, almond-milk, cola, soy-milk
5 different pets are kept: snake, turtle, mouse, ferret, goat

1. the egyptian is the person who likes coral
2. the russian is the owner of the snake
3. the person drinking iced-mirinda is the person who likes fuchsia
4. the dutch is the person drinking mirinda
5. the person who likes fuchsia is to the right of the person who likes light-brown
6. the havana-smoker is the owner of the goat
7. the montecristo-smoker is the person who likes chestnut
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle
9. the chinese is on the far left
10. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle
11. the montecristo-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the ferret
12. the bolivar-smoker is the person drinking cola
13. the italian is the dannemann-smoker
14. the chinese is to the left or right of the person who likes brown

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   chinese	|    dutch	|     egyptian	|    russian	|    italian	|
| Color		|    chestnut	|      brown	|      coral	|     light-brown	|     fuchsia	|
| Beverage	|     soy-milk	|      mirinda	|      almond-milk	| cola	|     iced-mirinda	|
| Cigar		|     montecristo	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| bolivar	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     turtle	|     ferret	|     goat	|     snake	|     mouse	|
